By: Swâmi Brahmânanda
---
The Name of the Lord purifies both body and soul. ‘I have taken the Name
of God; what have I to fear? what in this world can bind me? I have become
immortal in taking the Name of the Lord.' It is with this ardent faith that
one must perform the spiritual exercises.
